---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="About Me"
    description="About Ved Gupta (innovatorved) - Cloud Engineer and developer who writes code. Full Stack, Generative AI, Azure, React, Next.js, TypeScript, Docker, and Kubernetes."
>
    <section>
        <h1 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tighter">About Me</h1>
        <p>
            Hi there! I'm a Cloud Engineer and developer who writes code as much
            as I design infrastructure. My journey started in freelancing, where
            I built hands-on expertise in React, Next.js, JavaScript, and
            TypeScript across diverse client projects.
            <br /><br />
            I transitioned into a full-time Cloud Engineer role at LTIMindtree,
            where I design and deploy scalable Azure IaaS solutions and also
            build AI-powered apps and agents using Azure OpenAI — writing the
            application code, not just configuring the infrastructure around it.
            <br /><br />
            Beyond client work, I build open-source AI tools myself, end to end
            — including Subtitle Generator (an automatic video transcription CLI
            with 428+ GitHub stars, published on PyPI) and Realtime Interview
            Copilot (a real-time AI assistant using live audio transcription,
            73+ stars).
            <br /><br />
            Certified: Microsoft Azure AI Apps and Agents Developer Associate,
            Azure Administrator Associate, Azure AI Fundamentals, Google Cloud
            Associate Cloud Engineer.
            <br /><br />
            If you're interested in discussing Cloud, Generative AI, or Full
            Stack opportunities, feel free to connect here or reach out at{" "}
            <a
                href="mailto:me@vedgupta.in"
                data-event="contact_email_click"
                data-email="me@vedgupta.in"
                class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline"
            >
                me@vedgupta.in
            </a>.
        </p>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
